{"tid":1382290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「新戰術建議」前線：「報人數」，眾：「仲有我」","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T15:20:22.000Z","uid":114801,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0a97ff74edbe870cd7476f1268031fd185300626","tid":1382290,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"唔洗企前面都知，現場係唔會有時間上網慢慢睇資訊。<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望建議一個方法比前線評估仲有幾多人響後面。<br />\n<br />\nQ:點解唔用「光復香港，時代革命」？<br />\nA: 我希望有一個確實既代號比前線有需要果陣用來評估人數，唔想混淆遊行口號同代號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ:如果d人唔覆咁點算？<br />\nA:呢層希望現場人士幫幫手，當前線係度叫「報人數」果陣，只要你唔係準備緊離開，你有義務幫手嗌「仲有我」<br />\n<br />\nQ:仲有咩其他作用？<br />\nA: 激勵士氣，你幻想自己在現場聽到一班人嗌「仲有我」，有穩定軍心之效。"},{"pid":"a3d6153d67f25bc96d45e32bef07742918aadd9b","tid":1382290,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2a308c0c48abbce745a2fa5d7c4b4bc66ec5a8","tid":1382290,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"試一次先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">報人數</span>"},{"pid":"e6bdd2f27b864dbf9652fe9d8d12a89b2ebbf0c7","tid":1382290,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"好似撞機咁得唔得<br />\n一個叫1<br />\n下一個就叫2"},{"pid":"48def2ad6af4ea2c33627b751c32dedf663471d1","tid":1382290,"uid":246118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c2a308c0c48abbce745a2fa5d7c4b4bc66ec5a8","tid":1382290,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"試一次先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">報人數</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:34:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有我</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211f18416b08ccd74b83838b5c7d6e7101fc48d6","tid":1382290,"uid":11154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu